{"tid":979221,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【有一種悲傷改詞】妳的生日 （粵語招唱）","createTime":"2019-01-12T14:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T21:02:40.000Z","uid":48498,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2db7ce7f213706f1369645f19eed094677c61c1a","tid":979221,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:11:07.000Z","msg":"記掛一起睡眠<br />\n記掛當天 笑臉<br />\n說了分開 共誰 錄影片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慣了天天無眠<br />\n何來特別 懷緬<br />\n今年這日 將來這日 難免<br />\n<br />\n在妳的生日<br />\n寂寞無眠地寫出可笑的筆墨<br />\n歐洲那故事 只配在心中永誌<br />\n在這中止<br />\n<br />\n在妳的生日<br />\n日月如流像倒影 怎抹走都沒法消失<br />\n一直以來 感謝妳在 陪我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOh<br />\n願妳這生歡樂 縱不可 伴妳這生歡樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒法可放手 oh~<br />\n於妳的生日 無法不哭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒法可糾纏<br />\n相簿裏凝住的 幀幀記憶 生日這一天<br />\n竟在最後 只剩這日 懷緬<br />\n<br />\n在妳的生日<br />\n日月如流像倒影 怎抹走都沒法消失<br />\n一直以來 感謝妳在 陪我"},{"pid":"f4bdca7115beb71e3fc9e9cbf878c0d8002a024f","tid":979221,"uid":12754,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"content : 3/7<br />\norganization : 3/7<br />\nlanguage : 4/7<br />\n<br />\n中品作品<br />\n繼續努力"},{"pid":"89965ab1b424abbe57fe02345402d0110f185a78","tid":979221,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"包包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5902a170ee97dfad084cde23ca1a87a9bcc87114","tid":979221,"uid":48498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f4bdca7115beb71e3fc9e9cbf878c0d8002a024f","tid":979221,"uid":12754,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"content : 3/7<br />\norganization : 3/7<br />\nlanguage : 4/7<br />\n<br />\n中品作品<br />\n繼續努力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"多謝評分同支持，係真人真事尋晚瞓唔著寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9727505f64288c1ab60f0e7bc2c8a85479a7393c","tid":979221,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89965ab1b424ab